  "combined_text": "--- Main Page ---\nSeven Acre BarNGrill\nScroll\nLOCATION\n850 Hickory Flat Rd.\nMilton, GA 30004\nGet Directions\nHOURS\nMonday – Sun | 11:30am- 9:00pm\nFirst Come, First Served | No Reservations\nCONTACT\n770-777-2273\n– 7 Acre BarNGrill –\n[ BACKYARD GARDEN TO TABLE ]\n7 Acre BarNgrill is located in the familiar building at Birmingham Crossroads, which used to be a general store build in the 1930s and most recently Wilbur & Rudy’s Farmtable. The brainchild of Chris Sedgwick, 7 Acre BarNgrill features a 93 seat family-centric space and patio seating for 43. The menu is simple and includes comfort foods, a full bar featuring 77 whiskeys from around the world, homemade pies and real “garden to fork” ingredients demanded around here. Expect to see local, fresh, and hand-crafted cuisine and make sure to check out our 7 Acre garden- right in our backyard!\n– To Eat & Drink –\n[ Featuring our Seasonal favorites ]\nMenu\nKids Menu\nDessert Menu\n– straight from the garden –\nkeep up with everything\n7 acre\nEmail Address\nSign Up\nThank you!\nStay Social\nFind us on Facebook & Instagram!\nInstagram\nFacebook\nView fullsize\nView fullsize\nView fullsize\nView fullsize\n\n--- Page: /menu ---\nMenu — Seven Acre BarNGrill\n– To Eat & Drink –\n[ Featuring our Seasonal favorites ]\nMenu\nKids Menu\nDessert Menu\n\n--- Page: /s/7-Acre-Kids-Menu-20250410.pdf ---\n%PDF-1.3\n%���������\n4 0 obj\n<< /Filter /FlateDecode /Length 100332 >>\nstream\nx\u0001���Φ�q��}]��\u0001�9p���\u0003��EK\r�m\b�\u0001\u0002^���8Hlq�H\tF�2m�~��G��V�ᡤ�7d��2�9\"#�������w��������?����ݿ�ww��������\u0007��r����������������\u001f~y������'��\u001f\u001f�����<}�~x�7�~���?|�����������k��O?���O��o\u001f������\u000f���|������\u0007_\u001f\u001e�����������O�|a��z��}�{x{�|���q��������ӟ?���_��ow���{��}�����\u0017ww����w?�\u001f?����\t6�\u00176�vqw�\u0019\u0001�?�?��|�����Ǉ��\u000f\u000f��统���wo����?���w�n��f{?����w��m�`y\u001b��埯���P\u0010\u0011���;��>��,�x��\u001f��{��������\u0015�~��_